text: Gateway is a 1938 American drama movie directed by Alfred L. Werker and starring Don Ameche, Arleen Whelan, Gregory Ratoff, Binnie Barnes, John Carradine, Harry Carey, Lyle Talbot, Warren Hymer, Russell Hicks, Gilbert Ronald. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * Category:1938 drama movies Category:1930s American drama movies Category:20th Century Fox movies Category:Movies directed by Alfred L.
